Community Generated Templates

  • ml-template-azure

    This template can be used for easily setting up a data science or machine learning project with automated training and deployment using [GitHub Actions](https://github.com/features/actions) and [Azure Machine Learning](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/machine-learning/).

    docs

  • aml-template

    This template shows the more extensive capabilities of using GitHub Actions with Azure Machine Learning managing a machine learning project with automated training and deployment.

    docs

  • fastai/fastpages

    An easy to use blogging platform, with support for Jupyter notebooks, Word docs, and Markdown.

    docs

See the GitHub Template help documentation for instructions on how to use a template for your repo.
